episodes.title: Cult Life: On the Other Side of Scientology
episodes.description: Scientology is a monster.     Los Angeles based actor Doug Kramer talks about how the cult was part of his life since childhood. Now being free from it, he is working to heal from the trauma it brought to his life and is helping others through his YouTube channel, Dazed but Not Confused. Doug's videos are raw, insightful and often times hilarious monologues about his life and the evil insanity of this monster of cults.
